                        <h2>About the <span>Managing Director</span></h2>
                        <p>Elizabeth Alviar-Vidanes, the visionary founder and managing director of VCM, has dedicated
                            over 30 years to mastering the art of talent management and brand partnerships. From her
                            early days at Viva Films to leading VCM for over two decades, she has helped thousands of
                            brands find their ideal celebrity endorsers.</p>
                        <p class="m-0">Her deep passion for connecting brands with the right talent continues to drive
                            VCM's success, making them a trusted name in the industry. Under her leadership, VCM has
                            become synonymous with excellence in celebrity endorsements and marketing campaigns.</p>
